- Material: acrylic board/PP material
- Product Power Supply: DV 5V-1A
- Rated power: 3W
- Product size: 25*12*14cm
- Rated voltage: 220V 110-220V

Features：
The mosquito-loving 368nm ultraviolet light trapping lamp, 360-degree light, reacts with the photocatalytic photocatalyst to release carbon dioxide and airflow, simulating the moisture of the carbon dioxide emitted by the human body, and attracting mosquitoes and flies in any direction.
Strong suction: The fan stirs the surrounding air to form a vortex, so that the mosquitoes that are used to flying with the air flow come with the wind. When the mosquito approaches the wind tunnel, it will be sucked into the bottom mosquito trap by the strong vortex.
Removable structural design: Rotate counterclockwise to disassemble the mosquito storage box, wash it with water, and wipe it clean with a dry cloth after cleaning.
Environmentally friendly mute: purely physical killing mosquitoes, comfortable and quiet, no radiation, also suitable for children, pregnant women, the elderly.
Low-voltage energy-saving, power-saving - USB cable can be directly connected to mobile phone charger, charging treasure, laptop, computer case, USB socket, camping, night fishing, outdoor activities can be carried around to prevent mosquito nuisance.

Usage method：
1. Insert the power plug into the power socket, turn on the power supply and turn on the switch.
2. When not in use, cut off the power supply and pull out the power plug.
3. Before cleaning the mosquito storage room, the plug of power cord should be pulled out first, then the mosquito storage room should be unloaded, the residue in the room should be cleaned up, and then re-loaded into the rotary tightening.
4. Use at home, as long as the mosquito killer is scheduled several hours before bedtime, when you sleep, mosquitoes have basically been cleared, can be closed or moved to other rooms. If there are more indoor furniture, the time of mosquito hiding is different, and the time of mosquito killing may be longer.
5. When used in offices, business places or in the field, the mosquito killer can be turned on in the evening, and the mosquito can be basically eliminated by turning off the lights overnight.
6. After the mosquitoes are caught, do not immediately unplug the power supply, let the fan continue to operate until the mosquitoes are dehydrated and dried to death.

1 x Mosquito Killer Lamp
1 x USB Cable
1 x Acrylic board

Features：
The mosquito-loving 368nm ultraviolet light trapping lamp, 360-degree light, reacts with the photocatalytic photocatalyst to release carbon dioxide and airflow, simulating the moisture of the carbon dioxide emitted by the human body, and attracting mosquitoes and flies in any direction.
Strong suction: The fan stirs the surrounding air to form a vortex, so that the mosquitoes that are used to flying with the air flow come with the wind. When the mosquito approaches the wind tunnel, it will be sucked into the bottom mosquito trap by the strong vortex.
Removable structural design: Rotate counterclockwise to disassemble the mosquito storage box, wash it with water, and wipe it clean with a dry cloth after cleaning.
Environmentally friendly mute: purely physical killing mosquitoes, comfortable and quiet, no radiation, also suitable for children, pregnant women, the elderly.

Usage method：
1. Insert the power plug into the power socket, turn on the power supply and turn on the switch.
2. When not in use, cut off the power supply and pull out the power plug.
3. Before cleaning the mosquito storage room, the plug of power cord should be pulled out first, then the mosquito storage room should be unloaded, the residue in the room should be cleaned up, and then re-loaded into the rotary tightening.
4. Use at home, as long as the mosquito killer is scheduled several hours before bedtime, when you sleep, mosquitoes have basically been cleared, can be closed or moved to other rooms. If there are more indoor furniture, the time of mosquito hiding is different, and the time of mosquito killing may be longer.
5. When used in offices, business places or in the field, the mosquito killer can be turned on in the evening, and the mosquito can be basically eliminated by turning off the lights overnight.
6. After the mosquitoes are caught, do not immediately unplug the power supply, let the fan continue to operate until the mosquitoes are dehydrated and dried to death.

Specifications：
- Power cord length: 1.2M
- Material: acrylic board/PP material
- Product Power Supply: DV 5V-1A
- Rated power: 3W
- Product size: 25*12*14cm
- Rated voltage: 220V 110-220V

Features：
The mosquito-loving 368nm ultraviolet light trapping lamp, 360-degree light, reacts with the photocatalytic photocatalyst to release carbon dioxide and airflow, simulating the moisture of the carbon dioxide emitted by the human body, and attracting mosquitoes and flies in any direction.
Strong suction: The fan stirs the surrounding air to form a vortex, so that the mosquitoes that are used to flying with the air flow come with the wind. When the mosquito approaches the wind tunnel, it will be sucked into the bottom mosquito trap by the strong vortex.
Removable structural design: Rotate counterclockwise to disassemble the mosquito storage box, wash it with water, and wipe it clean with a dry cloth after cleaning.
Environmentally friendly mute: purely physical killing mosquitoes, comfortable and quiet, no radiation, also suitable for children, pregnant women, the elderly.
Low-voltage energy-saving, power-saving - USB cable can be directly connected to mobile phone charger, charging treasure, laptop, computer case, USB socket, camping, night fishing, outdoor activities can be carried around to prevent mosquito nuisance.

Usage method：
1. Insert the power plug into the power socket, turn on the power supply and turn on the switch.
2. When not in use, cut off the power supply and pull out the power plug.
3. Before cleaning the mosquito storage room, the plug of power cord should be pulled out first, then the mosquito storage room should be unloaded, the residue in the room should be cleaned up, and then re-loaded into the rotary tightening.
4. Use at home, as long as the mosquito killer is scheduled several hours before bedtime, when you sleep, mosquitoes have basically been cleared, can be closed or moved to other rooms. If there are more indoor furniture, the time of mosquito hiding is different, and the time of mosquito killing may be longer.
5. When used in offices, business places or in the field, the mosquito killer can be turned on in the evening, and the mosquito can be basically eliminated by turning off the lights overnight.
6. After the mosquitoes are caught, do not immediately unplug the power supply, let the fan continue to operate until the mosquitoes are dehydrated and dried to death.

1 x Mosquito Killer Lamp
1 x USB Cable
1 x Acrylic board
